ranges.text:
This command is specifically designed to work perfectly for anyone, you can use it to add an emoji by using a url by running H-upload <URL> <emoji name>.
You can also use it by sending an image as an attachment by running H-upload <emoji name> (while also attaching an image to the message).

data.caption: An example of how the command works when using a URL.
An example on how the command works when using an image attachment.
